[% META title = 'Rake' %]

<p>Mooncoin does collect rake in order to maintain our hosting, improve our code and add new features. 

<p><b>We do our best to offer the best rates.</b></p>
<p><b>Our current rake is under 1 percent.</b></p>

<p>We do not charge rake if the hand ends on the first betting round - before the flop.</p>

<div style="border: solid 1px; padding: 10px; width: 500px;">
